<lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ξένος θ’ ὅς ἡμῖν πο</supplied><unclear>μπ</unclear>ὸ<unclear>ς</unclear> ἦν θ<unclear>ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ωρίας.</supplied>
<lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">πρῶτον μὲν οὖν ποι</supplied>ηρὸ<unclear>ν</unclear> <hi rend="diaeresis">ἳ</hi>ζομ<unclear>εν</unclear> <supplied reason="lost">νάπος</supplied>
<lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">τά τ’ ἐκ ποδῶν σιγη</supplied>λὰ καὶ γλώσσ<unclear>η</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ς ἄπο</supplied>
</ab></div>
